	<!-- news -->
    <section class="testimonials" id="news">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="wow bounceInLeft animated animated" data-wow-delay="0.1s" style="visibility: visible;-webkit-animation-delay: 0.1s; -moz-animation-delay: 0.1s; animation-delay: 0.1s;"> 
				<h2>News</h2> 
			</div>
			<!-- row -->
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">					
					<div class="col-sm-12">
						<ul>	
							
							<li><p><strong>2021.01.</strong> I am awarded with <strong>DATA SCIENCE NGS SCHOLARSHIP and started my PhD career in National University of Singapore</strong>.</p></li>							
							<li><p><strong>2020.06.</strong> I am awarded with <strong>Outstanding graduate of School of Aerospace Engineering, Tsinghua University</strong>.</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.10.</strong> I am awarded with <strong>Scholarship of Second Prize in Tsinghua University</strong>, which is awarded to TOP 5% students in Tsinghua University.</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.09.</strong> I start to work as a Teaching Assistant for Theoretical Mechanics in Tsinghua University for the second time.</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.08.</strong> Our paper <i>"An efficient multibody dynamic model of three-dimensional meshing contacts in helical gear-shaft system and its solution."</i> is accepted by <strong>Mechanism and Machine Theory (SCI source, Q1)</strong>.</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.08.</strong> I will attend <strong>Chinese Congress of Theoretical and Applied Mechanics (CCTAM)</strong> from Aug. 25 to Aug. 28 in Hangzhou, China and welcome to approach me and chat!</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.07.</strong> I will attend ECCOMAS 2019 Multibody Dynamic Conference from July 14 to July 19 in Duisburg, Germany and welcome to approach me and chat!</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.02.</strong> Our paper <i>"Dynamic characteristics of helical gear based on Arbitrary Lagrangian Eulerian formulation."</i> is accepted by <strong>ECCOMAS 2019 Multibody Dynamic Conference</strong>.</p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2019.01.</strong> I have successfully completed the project cooperated with Mitsubishi Heavy Industries, Japan. I am the leader in this project, namely <i>"Development of evaluation method for sliding wear by multibody dynamics".</i> </p></li>
							<li><p><strong>2018.09.</strong> I start to work as a Teaching Assistant for Theoretical Mechanics in Tsinghua University.</p></li>							
							<li><p><strong>2018.09.</strong> I start my Master study at Tsinghua University, China, supervised by Prof. Gexue Ren!</p></li>
                            				<li><p><strong>2018.06.</strong> I graduate from Honors College, Northwestern Polytechnical University, China!</p></li>
                            				<li><p><strong>2018.01.</strong> I start to work as a Research Assistant in Multibody Dynamics Laboratory, Tsinghua University (THU), China, supervised by Prof. Gexue Ren, until my graduation in THU (expected in 2020.07).</p></li>
                        			</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- ./row -->		
		</div>
	</section>
